Just in case if you want it, you can use parametrized test here:
  @ParameterizedTest
  @ValueSource(strings = {TEXT_WITH_SINGLE_QUOTES,
      TEXT_WITH_DOUBLE_QUOTES, 
      TEXT_WITH_ID_QUOTED,
      TEXT_WITH_END_QUOTED
  })
  void test(String text) {
    UseCaseEngine.runTest(text, List.of(), Map.of());
  }

